== 其他立陶宛旗帜 ==
[[File:Naval_Ensign_of_Lithuania.svg|thumb]]
[[File:Flag_of_the_President_of_Lithuania.svg|thumb]]

立陶宛从1992年开始使用[[军舰旗|军舰旗]]，采用带蓝色十字架的白色背景，左上角是国旗图案。军舰旗长宽比为二比一，十字架宽度为所在边长的七分之一。<ref name="naval">{{cite web | work = [[国旗列表|Flags of the World]] | url = https://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/lt-nav.html | title = Lithuania - Naval Flags | accessdate = 2020-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200822211142/https://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/lt-nav.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-08-27}}</ref>。该旗曾是[[考那斯水庫|考纳斯游艇俱乐部]]的旗帜，不过当时的长宽比是三比二<ref>{{cite web | work = Flags of the World | url = https://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/lt_flgg.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200822211449/https://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/lt_flgg.html | title = Lithuania - Flags from "Flaggenbuch | accessdate = 2020-08-27 | archivedate = 2020-08-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[海上用旗|舰首旗]]与立陶宛政府用旗相同，该国海军舰艇还采用三角形舰首旗<ref name="naval" />。

1993年，[[立陶宛议会|立陶宛议会]]正式确定[[立陶宛统治者列表|立陶宛总统]]旗，采用暗红色背景，中间是国徽图案，长宽比为1.2比1<ref>Article 7(3), Law I-56, as amended</ref><ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2020-08-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200806125137/https://www.e-tar.lt/portal/lt/legalActEditions/TAR.438A78A26F38?faces-redirect=true | url = https://www.e-tar.lt/portal/lt/legalActEditions/TAR.438A78A26F38 | title = Lietuvos Respublikos Prezidento įstatymas | accessdate = 2020-08-27 | date = 1993-01-26 | publisher = Lietuvos Respublikos Seimas | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

立陶宛各县均有县旗且遵丛相同的图案格局：蓝色背景，四周有十个金色[[洛林十字|洛林十字]]（与国徽骑士盾牌上的十字相同），中间是该县自定的标志，大部分就是县徽<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200224194703/http://www.vexilla-mundi.com/lithuania_divisions.html | archivedate = 2020-02-24 | url = http://www.vexilla-mundi.com/lithuania_divisions.html | title = Vexillology of Lithuania | work = Vexilla Mundi | accessdate = 2020-08-27}}</ref>。

